# Cursor

Project guide: `AGENTS.md` / `.cursor/AGENTS.md` (symlinks to `CLAUDE.md`).

## Tooling (`.cursor/`)

- `cli.json` -- project permissions (translated from `.claude/settings.json`;
  `Shell(...)` mirrors Claude's `Bash(...)` allowlist).
- `hooks.json` -- `postToolUse` on `Write|StrReplace` and `afterFileEdit` on
  `Write|TabWrite` via shared `check-source.sh`.
- `hooks/` -- symlink to `.claude/hooks/`.
- `skills/` -- symlink to `.claude/skills/`. Invoke `cpp-style-review` /
  `python-style-review` after editing `cpp/`/`gtests/` or `modmesh/`/`tests/`.
- `statusline.sh` -- symlink to `.claude/statusline.sh`; set
  `statusLine.command` in `~/.cursor/cli-config.json`.

Build, test, lint, architecture, and style rules live in the root guide and
`STYLE.md`.
